msgid "Customizing the mouse cursor"
msgstr "自定义鼠标光标"

msgid ""
"You might want to change the appearance of the mouse cursor in your game in "
"order to suit the overall design. There are two ways to customize the mouse "
"cursor:"
msgstr ""
"你可能希望更改游戏中鼠标光标的外观，以便适应总体设计。自定义鼠标光标有两种方"
"法："

msgid "Using project settings. This is simpler, but more limited."
msgstr "使用项目设置。这种方式更简单，但功能也更有限。"

msgid "Using a script. This is more customizable, but involves scripting."
msgstr "使用脚本。这种方式更加可定制化，但需要编写脚本。"

msgid ""
"If you have to use the \"software\" approach, consider adding an "
"extrapolation step to better display the actual mouse input."
msgstr ""
"如果你必须使用“软件”的做法，可以考虑添加一个外推步骤，以便更好地显示实际的鼠"
"标输入。"

msgid "Using project settings"
msgstr "使用项目设置"

msgid ""
"Open the **Project Settings** and go to **Display > Mouse Cursor**. You will "
"see the settings :ref:`Custom Image <class_ProjectSettings_property_display/"
"mouse_cursor/custom_image>`, :ref:`Custom Image Hotspot "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_display/mouse_cursor/custom_image_hotspot>`, "
"and :ref:`Tooltip Position Offset <class_ProjectSettings_property_display/"
"mouse_cursor/tooltip_position_offset>`."
msgstr ""
"打开\\ **项目设置**\\ 并进入\\ **显示 > 鼠标光标**\\ 。你将看到以下设置："
"\\ :ref:`自定义图像 <class_ProjectSettings_property_display/mouse_cursor/"
"custom_image>`\\ 、\\ :ref:`自定义热点图像 "
"<class_ProjectSettings_property_display/mouse_cursor/custom_image_hotspot>` "
"和\\ :ref:`工具提示位置偏移 <class_ProjectSettings_property_display/"
"mouse_cursor/tooltip_position_offset>`\\ 。"

msgid "On the web platform, the maximum allowed cursor image size is 128×128."
msgstr "在 web 平台上，允许的最大光标图像大小为 128×128。"

msgid "Using a script"
msgstr "使用脚本"

msgid "Create a Node and attach the following script."
msgstr "创建一个 Node 节点并附加下面的脚本。"

msgid ""
"Check :ref:`Input.set_custom_mouse_cursor() "
"<class_Input_method_set_custom_mouse_cursor>`'s documentation for more "
"information on usage and platform-specific caveats."
msgstr ""
"检查 :ref:`Input.set_custom_mouse_cursor() "
"<class_Input_method_set_custom_mouse_cursor>` 的文档，以获取有关使用和平台特"
"定注意事项的更多信息。"

msgid "Cursor list"
msgstr "光标列表"

msgid ""
"There are multiple mouse cursors you can define, documented in "
"the :ref:`Input.CursorShape <enum_Input_CursorShape>` enum. Which ones you "
"want to use depends on your use case."
msgstr ""
"你可定义多种鼠标光标，详见 :ref:`Input.CursorShape <enum_Input_CursorShape>` "
"枚举类型。具体选择取决于你的使用场景。"
